wiki.content:
"The Captain" is a newer and more polished version of the song "Help Me Become Captain" by Biffy Clyro. "The Captain" was released on the 26th October 2009 and is included on the band's fifth album Only Revolutions. It became the band's sixth top 20 single after it entered the UK singles chart at number 17.
